  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Cold Bite!<br><br>Cold Bite is a top-down shooter in which the player fights endless waves of zombies. Build turrets, level-up, and hold them off as long as you can!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1027200/extras/de2e9b788d8e2511e148da19e020619a.poster.avif?t=1594928735\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1027200/extras/de2e9b788d8e2511e148da19e020619a.webm?t=1594928735\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1027200/extras/de2e9b788d8e2511e148da19e020619a.mp4?t=1594928735\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Build turrets to aid you in your fight.<br></li><li>Level-up and distribute points into speed, money, and fire rate.<br></li><li>Fight to the end... if you can.</li></ul><br>Cold Bite also supports saving/loading, so you can continue where you left off. <br><br>How long can you survive?",
